---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const updated = '2025-01-01';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Longhorn Supply & Provision privacy policy. What we collect, how we use it, and who we share it with. No medical data collected."
>
  <article class="container-rugged py-12 lg:py-16 max-w-3xl">
    <p class="font-display uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-copper text-xs mb-1">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="text-ink">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-charcoal/60">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="prose max-w-none mt-8 text-charcoal leading-relaxed space-y-5">
      <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 border-l-2 border-copper pl-3">
        This policy is provided as a starting template. Have it reviewed by an attorney before launch — especially if you intend to operate in California, the EU, or other regions with specific privacy statutes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-ink font-display uppercase tracking-tight mt-8 text-2xl">1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        Longhorn Supply &amp; Provision ("we", "us", "our") operates this website. We are a US-based supplier of research peptides and laboratory consumables.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-ink font-display uppercase tracking-tight mt-8 text-2xl">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect the following categories of information:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-1 pl-5 list-disc">
        <li><strong>Contact &amp; quote-request data:</strong> name, business or institutional email, phone, shipping ZIP, and the items in your quote.</li>
        <li><strong>Order data:</strong> shipping address, billing details, items ordered, lot numbers shipped.</li>
        <li><strong>Site analytics:</strong> standard server logs and (optionally) aggregate page-view analytics. No medical or health information is collected.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies / local storage:</strong> small data stored in your browser to remember age-gate acceptance and your quote list. We do not use cross-site advertising cookies.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-ink font-display uppercase tracking-tight mt-8 text-2xl">3. How We Use It</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-1 pl-5 list-disc">
        <li>To respond to quote requests and process orders.</li>
        <li>To verify researcher qualification where required.</li>
        <li>To fulfill, ship, and provide post-sale support including lot traceability and COA delivery.</li>
        <li>To improve the Site and our service.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-ink font-display uppercase tracking-tight mt-8 text-2xl">4. Who We Share It With</h2>
      <p>
        We share information only with service providers needed to operate the business: hosting (Netlify), email, shipping carriers, payment processors (out-of-band), and analytics. We do not sell personal information.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-ink font-display uppercase tracking-tight mt-8 text-2xl">5. No Health or Medical Information</h2>
      <p>
        We do not request or collect health or medical information. Please do not include any health details in correspondence with us. If you do, we will redact or discard it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-ink font-display uppercase tracking-tight mt-8 text-2xl">6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        We retain quote and order records as needed to provide service, meet tax and legal obligations, and resolve disputes. You may request deletion of your contact data by emailing <a href="mailto:privacy@longhornsupply.com" class="text-copper underline">privacy@longhornsupply.com</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-ink font-display uppercase tracking-tight mt-8 text-2xl">7. Your Choices</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-1 pl-5 list-disc">
        <li><strong>Browser storage:</strong> Clear your browser's local storage to reset the age gate and quote list.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Use your browser's controls to block or clear cookies. Core Site functions do not require advertising cookies.</li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> Unsubscribe links are included in any marketing emails. Order/quote correspondence is transactional.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-ink font-display uppercase tracking-tight mt-8 text-2xl">8. Security</h2>
      <p>
        We use commercially reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect information in our custody. No system is perfectly secure, and we make no warranty of absolute security.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-ink font-display uppercase tracking-tight mt-8 text-2xl">9. Children</h2>
      <p>
        The Site is restricted to adults aged 21 and older. We do not knowingly collect information from minors. If you believe a minor has provided information, contact us and we will delete it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-ink font-display uppercase tracking-tight mt-8 text-2xl">10. Updates</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date above will reflect the most recent change. Material changes will be noted on the Site.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-ink font-display uppercase tracking-tight mt-8 text-2xl">11. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about privacy? Email <a href="mailto:privacy@longhornsupply.com" class="text-copper underline">privacy@longhornsupply.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
